    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"380294\">Matt Diamond</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/about.20.20a.2Bb.2Bc.20.3D1.20then.20a.5E2.2Fb.20.2B.20b.5E2.2Fc.20.2B.20c.5E2.2Fa.20.E2.89.A5.201/near/508992483\">发言道</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>o you mean that the left side of the <code>or</code> is true if <code>a = b = c</code> and the right side is true if <code>¬(a = b = c)</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>yes</p>",
