    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"750070\">Wang Jingting</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/about.20.20a.2Bb.2Bc.20.3D1.20then.20a.5E2.2Fb.20.2B.20b.5E2.2Fc.20.2B.20c.5E2.2Fa.20.E2.89.A5.201/near/508992513\">发言道</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ou can probably try to show that a^2/b + b^2 / c + c^2 / a &lt;= 1 if and only if a = b = c. I guess this is a more accurate lean version than what you demonstrated above?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It looks like more complicated , But this is also a good idea，thanks</p>",
